window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Goethe's masterpiece and perhaps the greatest work in German literature, <i>Faust</i> has made the legendary German alchemist one of the central myths of the Western world. Here indeed is a monumental Faust, an audacious man boldly wagering with the devil, Mephistopheles, that no magic, sensuality, experience or knowledge can lead him to a moment he would wish to last forever. </p>"; 
